## GET /v1/user/following{?user_id,restrict}
Get users that user followed.

+ Parameters
    + user_id: `3623925` (integer, required) - User ID.
    + restrict: `public` (enum[string], required) - Restrict for user's accessible.
        + Members:
            + `public`
            + `private`
    + offset: `30` (integer, optional) - Offset index.

