## GET /v2/user/list
Get users that user blocked.

+ Parameters
    + filter: `for_ios` (string, optional) - Filter for store vendors.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
        }



## GET /v1/user/me/state
Get logged-in user's statuses.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "user_state": {
            "is_mail_authorized": true,
            "has_changed_pixiv_id": true,
            "can_change_pixiv_id": false
          }
        }



